\id 2PE - Ekajuk New Testament 
\h 2 Pita 
\toc1 2 Pita 
\toc2 2 Pit 
\mt2 2 NWER NYI 
\mt1 PITA 
\c 1  
\nb  
\v 1 Me Saimon Pita ji li nlokeltum no Jisos Kraist, a ntiingetib ewe, n kpꞌnyono nwer nyia tv ane ba ma bel ekakesehk ji nno a nno ana wahr, tib eno alehke ji Esowo, a ji Jisos Kraist ntꞌtahre ewahre fvfo.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Jon 16:10; Rom 9:30\f* 
\p  
\v 2 Nong, nnoobo, a elkoono jol go egahne ellong gbꞌgbal, go elkahne ni ń kpꞌkahne Esowo, a Jisos Ntul ewahre. 
\s1 Nsol nyi kpo tib eltaame 
\p  
\v 3 Esowo go ege a nsahm wo, á ma-r ka ejum ajehng ajehng ji li ka elkpin nfenfe, ji nne bahke koko, jol Esowo Esowo, tib go elkahne ni e kpꞌkahne nne noo no lung-r no tv elne re wahr jol go ege ellub, fere bel nnoobo enye.  
\v 4 Ano wo wahnge á ma nyam egburu enyam bi nno a nno tong-r, eji ń lꞌjol jang jang ana Esowo, ń lꞌtaame tv enyam bio, tib eji ḿ ma for go elbolo ni njini nyia ma bol. Nsol nyi kpo melle ane go bo a ntim re bo jo lim, nyi nyi ma wahng njini ma jol ano. 
\p  
\v 5 Esi jꞌnehm ana ji, nobo re wahn jo nok mbang anyehng anyehng, jo ko nnoobo budu go egahne eltaame, fere ko elkahne budu go egahna nnoobo,  
\v 6 fere jo bob elnahne antahng budu go egahne elkahne, fere jo ko elkpuumu budu go elbobo elnahne antahng, fere ko eltoono ni ń kpꞌtoono Esowo budu go egahne elkpuumu,  
\v 7 fere ko elkoro ni abonane ejahne kpo kor-n budu go egahne eltoono ni ń kpꞌtoono Esowo, fere ko elkoro ni ane kpee kp-n koro budu go egahne elkoro ni abonane ejahne kpo kor-n.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Gal 5:6,22\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Ń lꞌbel nsol nyia, lꞌjol gbalee, ń nehm tiki jol akooko ane ba ma demme go elkahne nio ni ń kpꞌkahne Jisos Kraist Ntul ewahre.  
\v 9 Nne no tohko bel nsol nyia, yebwa amahr, á kpo nyehn advrehndv.\f + \fr 1:9 \ft 1 Jon 2:11\f* Yebyini re abiafem enye nya mahne mahne, bo m-e ru wohng go. 
\p  
\v 10 Abonanee, ano wo fvfo nobo re wahn gbehd, lohko jol ana Esowo ma-n lung, fere yehk-n re wahn jol. Ń lꞌlim ano, ń nehm tiki gbo.  
\v 11 Ana wo bahke wahnge Esowo bi kpi nnoobo ka-n nsahm nyi ḿ bahke ma yel go ejahbetul ji li go njinanjini, ji Jisos Kraist ntꞌtahre ewahre, a Ntul ewahre. 
\s1 Pita wo jolo nne no nyehne ellub ni Jisos go amahr 
\p  
\v 12 Esi jia ji wahnge n kpo kon-n nsol nyia buumu ngare anyehng anyehng, jol eji ń kpꞌkꞌkahn nsol nyia, ḿ ma fere yiimi tꞌtahne go etingitingi ji ń kpi no. 
\p  
\v 13 N kpꞌtiri re, nꞌnob eji n kpeke li go elkpin re me n mell-n, eji n kp-n buumu nsol nyia.  
\v 14 Tibre n kpꞌkahne re, m bahke gulu elkpoko, ana Jisos Kraist Ntul ewahre tib-m no.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Jon 21:18-19\f* 
\v 15 M bahke noko, lim mbang bum, eji ń lꞌjo buumu nsol nyia ngare nyi m ma tahm njini nyia sa. 
\p  
\v 16 Tibre e tohkem emongo ajehng ajehng ji wahr fumu no, eji e lennge nsahm nyi Jisos Kraist Ntul ewahre ka-n, a elbake ene ni á bahke bake. Wahr ba jolo ane ba nyehne njꞌjok ellub ene.  
\v 17 E jolo ona eji Esowo Nsoo ka-e ellub, fere tehk-e, ngare nyio nyi ellum lohngo go ellub nio ni nnen, ba tob-e, ni bungu re, “A wo li akor-m mmon ewame no kpo kor-m sꞌsehng.”\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Mat 17:5\f* 
\v 18 E wuku ellum ni lohngo go ejahbetul Esowo, tibre e jolo a ne go mbarebare ewong jio. 
\p  
\v 19 Ellum nio ebkpe yiimi ebung ji abanyehnamahr Esowo njahm gbalee, ji ji nobo re wahn jo kunu ekpu, tibre li ana etꞌrekahng ji kpꞌyake go edi ejannge tete efungfu se, elonlo ji efungfu kehme elyake go egahna ntim.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft Ell 22:6,16\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Go ngbokambang li re wahn kahn re, nnene limm, no bahke ma lennge enyehnamahr ji bo nyono go nwer Esowo antahng.  
\v 21 Tibre enyehnamahr ajehng ajehng limm, ji ane ko ba a ji, ana koro bo, sehngem ane ba etohko ji Esowo jo melle bo, bo ba jo bung alum Esowo.\f + \fr 1:21 \ft 2 Tim 3:16-17\f* 
\c 2  
\s1 Akimfahnge atꞌtibi 
\p  
\v 1 Akimfahnge abanyehnamahr tob woomo go ellong ane wuku wuku jang jang ana akimfahnge atꞌtibi bahke tob woomo go egahne ellong.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Mat 24:11; Elt 20:30\f* Bo bahke koko eltibi ni ki li go etingitingi, ni kpo bvvrv ba a ni, ba semme, fere ten Nde no gunu bo. Ano wo bahke wahnge bo rannge elbo elwaare.  
\v 2 Ane gbalee bahke toono mbang ebo, nyi li song kak go elrannge. Tib go bo esi wo bahke wahnge, ane jo bung ebi bada mbang nyi etingitingi.  
\v 3 Bo bahke jo baare amahr go nsol ane, fere jo tub-n aka nya bo fumu antahng, fere jo li-n nsehng. Ekidi eblab ji elam nong no kpi bo sik. Nne no bahke bo rannge kpehme tiki lal.  
\v 4 Eji babenjel limi abiafem, Esowo tahrem bo bum. Á rodo na bo, ro kak ebi edi, edi ji bo wob go agbekobo go ejannge, jehk kpꞌsiki efung elam.  
\v 5 Njini nyi mahne mahne, Esowo tahrem bum. Á tumu nnyel, nnyel ba bulu abi ane ba jolo go njini nyio. 
\p Á tahre Noa wo wo, ji jo tib ane ana bo bahke lehke eno go esamahr Esowo, fere tob tahre ane asehma bako fvfo.  
\v 6 Esowo lame Sodom a Gomorra, fere jahm kpee fi, sa atong atong, eji lꞌkꞌkpe tiki jol. Ane bao ba, Esowo ko re á tib abi ane bako ba bahke jini elliingi. 
\p  
\v 7 Á tahre Lot yake, ji jolo etingi nne, ye ji abi ane bao jo gbiing-e tib go bo ebi elkpin.  
\v 8 Eji etingi nne jio jolo a bo o, jo nyehn nsol ana nyio efung abehng abehng, fere jo wuk, jo maang-e go ege atahng sehng tib go abi nsol nya bo jo lim. 
\p  
\v 9 Jehova kpꞌkahne ana á kpo tahre ane ba kpꞌtoono mbang enye, yehke go elgaare,\f + \fr 2:9 \ft 1 Kor 10:13; Ell 3:10\f* fere kuuru abi ane, bo jo nyehn erem sik efung elam,  
\v 10 asehngesehnge ane bao ba kpo jen go nnyam a ngubjing, jo lim nsol nyi ki li saang, nyi kpo kor bo, fere jo daange atubesi. Akimfahnge atꞌtibi bao kpi esahb. Bo kpo lim akuuku. Ntul awohng awohng kpehme lub bo, bo kpo su na bo.  
\v 11 Jol enjel nyi gbale gbal, fere bel nsahm sehnge akimfahnge atꞌtibi bao, bo kpehme ka bo ebi go mbang elsuku, bo lꞌyiimi go esamahr bi Jehova.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Jud 9\f* 
\v 12 Ane bao kpo lim eljini ana ni enyam ekulugbe, bi ki kpi elkahne, bi bo jele bo re, bo jo bob bo, fere wul. Bo kpo su nsol nyi bo kil elkahne. Bo bahke kpoko tan ana enyam ekulugbe.  
\v 13 Bo bahke bele eltuuru ebo go abꞌbi nya bo kpo lim. Kpo kor bo re bo li nkak ngara njul, fere jo geere. Bo lꞌba woomo go egahne ellong, jo li nsol alehke, bo li ana adale nya li nne go ngubjing, a anyakenyake adehbe. Bo kpo li, fere jo bel eyebatahng eji bo kpꞌjene, jo nehm ane. 
\p  
\v 14 Amahr ebo ebsa go anebkal anebkal. Abiafem kpehme tiki gbal bo. Bo kpo were ane ba kpꞌdulu. Bobkpili amahr abaare mal kpee. Bo li ane ba Esowo ma demme bo.  
\v 15 Bobtan mbang, eji bo ma yaange mbang nyi nno sa, fere kpꞌsehnge go mbang nyehko. Bo kpi mbang nyi Belam toono, ji jolo mmon a Beor. Nsehng nyi abꞌbi alimi jo kor-e ellehke sehng.  
\v 16 Eji á limi abiafem, bo rehk-e rehke, tibre mbvankang nyi kil jo bung na, á bungu go ellum ni nne, fere kpan egboolo nnyehnamahr noo.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Jud 11; Ell 2:14\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Akimfahnge atꞌtibi bao li ana abing alahb nya ma ka, ana akparesemsem nya nfeb kpꞌtahle yannge a nya. Esowo ebtoobo edi nkom ejannge bum bo, ji bo bahke jolo go njinanjini.  
\v 18 Bo kpo bung alum elgeere, nya ki lohng ejumjum. Bo kpo ko asabsab nsol njini nya kpo kor ane go ellimi ba a nya, ba were ane ba kpꞌna lohngo go ellong ane ba wob go ejannge.  
\v 19 Bo kpo nyam tong bo re, bo bahke limi bo, bo for, jol eji bofono antahng li li aju ka nsol nyi li go njini nyia, nyi bahke rannge. Tib ejum ji kpi nne, ji ji nne li nju ka-e.\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Jon 8:34\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Eji nne ma for go asabsab nsol nya njini nyia, tib go elkahne ni á kpꞌkahne Ntul ewahre Jisos Kraist ji li ntꞌtahre, á lꞌkpe feere, song yel go nsol nyio, nsol nyio lꞌbob-e, á bahke kpe sab sehnge ana wuku wuku á jolo no.\f + \fr 2:20 \ft Mat 12:45\f* 
\v 21 Jol ga nob ka ane bao li re, bo kahnem mbang nyi etingitingi, sehnge re bo kahn etingitingi jio, kehm fere yake mbarebara ntahm nyi bo ka bo.\f + \fr 2:21 \ft Luk 12:47-48\f* 
\v 22 Eblohko lim bo ana bo kpo tub elgan re, “Mbv kpo feere, song kpu akahle nya á kahle no li.” Elgan nehko kpe li re, “Ekuk ji bo m-e wulu alahb, á kpo feere, song yel adob, jo bannge.” 
\c 3  
\s1 Elbake ni Jisos Ntul ewahre 
\p  
\v 1 Akpondahme enyame, a wo li etoono nwer nyi m ma nyon tv-n. Go nwer ebal ebal nyi m ma nyon tv-n, n sebe re me n mell-n ntir atahng enyahne nyi nno, eji m ma-n buumu nsol nyia.  
\v 2 N kpꞌsebe re me n buum-n alum nya abarebare abanyehnamahr Esowo bungu no mahne mahne, fere tob buum-n ntahm nyi e yake no ka-n, wahr ji li abatiingetib ba Ntul a Jisos ji li ntꞌtahre.  
\v 3 Nobo re wahn gbo mbang kahn re, esꞌkohro afung, ane bandiki bahke jolo, ba bahke jo lim ana ji bahke jo kor bofono antahng.\f + \fr 3:3 \ft 1 Tim 4:1\f* Bo bahke jo nyok-n re,  
\v 4 “Á nyame tong-n re, á bahke bake. Ye nona?\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Mat 24:48\f* Bomo ngare nyi babnsoo ejahre kpo no tete sik anv, njini ka tiki yaange, kpeke li ana jolo go ngare nyi Esowo limi no.” 
\p  
\v 5 Bo kpꞌfake asamahr ebo go nkpe, jol eji bo kpꞌnyehne etingitingi jia ji li re, Mahne mahne Esowo bꞌbung, elbung abola ndi kehm jolo. Ndi lohngo go alahb. Alahb ma á ko, lim ndi.  
\v 6 Alahb manehm ma bulu njini nyi mahne mahne, fere rannge kpee.  
\v 7 Ellum nꞌnehm ni Esowo bungu no, ni ni wahnge á ma kuuru elbung abola njini nyia kpꞌsiki efung bi á bahke jahme go agun. Á kpꞌkuuru njini nyia bum tete efung elam rehng, bi á bahke rannge abi ane.\f + \fr 3:7 \ft 2 Tes 1:8\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Akpondahme wahn, kana jo yini ejum ji n yahke bung a, tibre goji Jehova efung abehng li ana nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu. Nnya atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu li-e ana efung abehng.  
\v 9 Jehova kpehme laange ellimi ji á nyame no, ana egom jindiki kpo tir re, á kpo kunu afung afung. Jehova kpo kpooro, tibre á kpehme seb re nne awohng awohng kpo, tan.\f + \fr 3:9 \ft 1 Tim 2:4\f* Á kpꞌsebe re, ane kpee gbo ndon, sennge njahm go bo abiafem.  
\v 10 Efung bi Ntul a Jisos bahke bake, á bahke gbede na ana nwajv. Efung bio, egburu erehm bahke jolo, tib eji elbung bahke tane.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Ell 20:11; 21:1\f* Nsol nyi li o bahke nyane tib go elfuubu agun nio. Njini bahke fehke a nsol a nsol enye kpee.  
\v 11 Eji nsol nyio bahke nyane ano kpee, anv, ane aba fuumu re wahn jol? Belen elkpin ni li eje eje, wahn jol Esowo Esowo,  
\v 12 eji ń kpꞌsiki re efung bio bi Esowo kpir-n. Jo noken, goji efung bio lꞌgulu elbiingi,\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Mat 24:14; Rom 11:25\f* bi elbung bahke lulu, fere fi kpee, nsol nyi li o fere nyane tib go elfuubu agun nio.  
\v 13 Wo, wahr kpꞌsiki elbung ni nfenfe, a njini nyi nfenfe, nyi bahke jolo nob nob, ana Esowo nyame no. 
\p  
\v 14 Akpondahme wahn, eji ń kpꞌjehke sik efung bio, jo gbehden, wahn kꞌbel ebꞌbi ajehng ajehng go esamahr Esowo. Jolen go elkoono! 
\p  
\v 15 Koon elkpuumu ni Jisos Ntul ewahre ana eltahre enahne. Ano wo fvfo Pol ekorokoro mmonanne ejahre nyono no tv-n go elkahne ni Esowo ka-e no.  
\v 16 Á bungu bada nsol nyia kpee go ege awer nya á nyono no. Go awer nyao, nsol nyindiki nyia, nyi kpꞌriidi go elkahne. Ane ba kil kahne ejumjum, a ane ba kil toono mbang anyehng kpo rod alum nyao, jo kpiidi a nya. Bo kpo tob ko alum nyandiki nya wob go nwer Esowo, jo lim ano. Eji bo kpꞌlimi ano, bo kpi elbo rannge. 
\p  
\v 17 Akpondahme enyame, ń kpꞌkahne nsol nyia wuku wuku. Jo gberen elnahne, eji abi ane ba kil bumu ntahm anyehng anyehng lꞌki-n were, fere nehm-n, fere mell-n go adi nya ń jehk no.  
\v 18 Jo gbalen go nnoobo nyi Ntul a Jisos Kraist ntꞌtahre ewahre, wahn fere gbal go elkahne ene. Nong, ellub jol ka-e anv tete go njinanjini. Emen.